[
    {"title": "PopPop Symphony",  "artist": "DotDot Band",   "plays": 1200000, "genre": "Pop",  "rating": 4.9},
    {"title": "Async Pipeline",   "artist": "Pythonic",      "plays": 850000,  "genre": "Rock", "rating": 4.2},
    {"title": "Broken Track",     "artist": "Unknown",       "plays": 500,     "genre": "Pop",  "rating": "invalid_rating"},
    {"title": "Kernel Pop Beats", "artist": "MC Pipeline",   "plays": 2300000, "genre": "Pop",  "rating": 4.8},
    {"title": "Slow Jazz Chill",  "artist": "Blue Note",     "plays": 450000,  "genre": "Jazz", "rating": 3.9}
] >> raw_tracks.

raw_tracks >> Map(Track):
    (Track, "rating", (Track::rating >> Num >> Catch(err): 0.0 ..)) >> Set.
.. >> Filter(Track):
    Track::genre == "Pop" & Track::plays >= 1000000.
.. >> Sort(Track):
     -Track::plays.
.. >> List >> newTracks.

"==================================================" >> Display.
"🎵 POPPOP GLOBAL MUSIC HITS CHART 🏆" >> Display.
"==================================================" >> Display.

newTracks >> Map:
    "{@::title} ({@::artist}) - {@::plays} played [★{@::rating}]" >> Display.
..

"--------------------------------------------------" >> Display.
"⭐ ヒット楽曲平均評価点: {newTracks >> Map: @::rating .. >> Average}" >> Display.
"==================================================" >> Display.
